Hi, I found this is a doc problem rather than a bug. Please use `tooltip.axisPointer.animation: 0` to disable the animation.

```
option = {
    title: {
        text: 'Awesome Chart'
    },
    xAxis: {
        data: ['Sun', 'Mon', 'Tue', 'Wed', 'Thu', 'Fri', 'Sat']
    },
    yAxis: {},
    tooltip: {
        triggerOn: 'click',
        trigger: 'axis',
        transitionDuration: 0,
        show: true,
        axisPointer: {
            type: 'shadow',
            animation: 0,
        }
    },
    series: [{
        type: 'line',
        data: [220, 182, 191, 234, 290, 330, 310]
    }]
};
```

